title: About
text:
Hi there! Welcome to my ISSS608 Visual Analytics homepage!
I’m Sei Sar, a Master of IT in Business student at SMU. This website highlights my journey in learning Visual Analytics under the guidance of Professor Kam Tim Seong. The course features Hands-on Exercises, In-class Exercises, and Take Home Assignments that provide practical experience and deepen my understanding of this exciting new field that I am exploring. In this website, you will find my coursework prepared for this course.
